{
  "text": "In the next step we find (formal) solutions of Klein-Gordon and Dirac equations in two important cases (Section 4 of [CITATION_1] ). In one of them we use (as a tool during calculations) an additional algebra F and its representations. Specific calculations are made in [CITATION_2] (including the form of metric tensor, gamma matrices, representations of F and the solutions of Klein-Gordon and Dirac equations). For spin 0 particles the momenta P j = i\u2202 j . For spin 1/2 particles we set [CITATION_3] the momenta as",
